    <a href="/content/ryerson/calendar/2020-2021/courses/finance/FIN/710.html" title="FIN 710 - Advanced Corporate Finance" class="courseListCourseLink"><span class="courseListCourseCode">FIN 710</span> - <span class="courseListCourseName">Advanced Corporate Finance</span></a>
    
	
		<div class="courseListDescription">In this course, financial theory will be applied to a variety of corporate finance issues including capital structure policy, dividend policy, corporate valuation, securities valuation, risk management, option pricing applications and mergers and acquisitions. Practical solutions to real world financial issues will be explored.</div>
	
	
		<div class="courseListLength"><span class="courseInfoLabels">Weekly Contact: </span><span class="courseInfoValues">Lecture: 3 hrs. </span></div>
	
	
